<text top="43" left="279" width="162" height="49" font="0">Protocol</text>
<text top="131" left="70" width="145" height="18" font="2">Dot Blot Fabrication:</text>
<text top="153" left="102" width="492" height="16" font="3">Suitably modified peptides modeled on histone tails were obtained from Abcam.</text>
<text top="173" left="102" width="571" height="16" font="3">Each peptide is added to Bio-Dot apparatus at 0.01 and 0.1 ug / 50uL total volume (BioRad) </text>
<text top="193" left="102" width="175" height="16" font="3">Let sit on rocker 60 minutes.</text>
<text top="214" left="102" width="521" height="16" font="3">Pull through with vacuum, wash once with 100uL TBS and twice with 200uL TBSTw.</text>
<text top="234" left="102" width="502" height="16" font="3">Remove membrane from Bio-Dot and transfer to 10mL Pierce SuperBlock in tray.</text>
<text top="254" left="102" width="193" height="16" font="3">Place on rocker for 30 minutes.</text>
<text top="274" left="102" width="136" height="16" font="3">Dump off SuperBlock.</text>
<text top="295" left="70" width="252" height="18" font="2">Antibody hybridization and imaging:</text>
<text top="317" left="102" width="271" height="16" font="3">Add Primary Antibody in 10mL total volume.</text>
<text top="337" left="102" width="193" height="16" font="3">Place on rocker for 30 minutes.</text>
<text top="358" left="102" width="191" height="16" font="3">Wash 3 x 5 minutes in TBSTw.</text>
<text top="378" left="102" width="421" height="16" font="3">Add secondary antibody diluted in SuperBlock in 10mL total volume.</text>
<text top="398" left="102" width="193" height="16" font="3">Place on rocker for 30 minutes.</text>
<text top="418" left="102" width="343" height="16" font="3">Wash 3 x 15 minutes in TBSTw, 1 x 10 minutes in TBS.</text>
<text top="438" left="102" width="475" height="16" font="3">Image using ECL and a FluorChem Peltier-cooled camera (Cell Biosciences)</text>
</page>
